# ============================================================================
# Important: What SHOULD Be Committed
# ============================================================================
# DO commit:
# - README.md
# - DEPLOYMENT.md
# - TECHNICAL_NOTES.md
# - terraform/*.tf files
# - terraform/terraform.tfvars.example
# - terraform/inventory-template.tftpl
# - ansible/playbooks/*.yml
# - ansible/ansible.cfg (if created)
# - This .gitignore file
#
# DO NOT commit:
# - terraform/terraform.tfvars (contains your VPC IDs, IPs)
# - ansible/inventory/aws_windows.yml (auto-generated with IPs/passwords)
# - *.log files (may contain sensitive output)
# - AWS credentials or keys
# ============================================================================
ansible/terraform.tfstate*
